{{Youmay|a razor-sharp wire|[[monofilament cable]], a strong monofilament sometimes referred to as monofilament wire}}
'''Monofilament wire''' was a fiber so strong and thin that its cutting power was greater than that of the sharpest [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblade]]. Practically anything that touched it would be cut in two. These wires were favorite weapons of [[Assassin/Legends|assassins]].

A [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] named [[Sniquux]] used this wire to assassinate several [[t'landa Til]] priests on [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]], scaring them until they ran into his deadly trap.

Monofilament wires could be combined into a [[monofilament net]] to create an even deadlier trap.<ref name="Return to Ord Mantell">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Return to Ord Mantell]]''</ref>

